  "id": "RAW_79399e5c",
  "title": "时间、项目双维度，打造真正有用的工作笔记",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247601768&idx=2&sn=d4499dcc8b24ceb5f71d6692333df615",
  "date": "2025-12-21 01:07:00",
  "author": "少数派",
  "siteName": "少数派",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d715779b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRiaibld4uOgWmGSOcgP87ZxcorooSlJyB6nzNvLYBVzV1qBG5fIELHDpR2ybzgiaIPGT02v2PAlT0iawQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-weight: bold;\">编注</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">：我们会不定期挑选 Matrix 的优质文章，展示来自用户的最真实的体验和观点。文章代表作者个人观点，少数派仅对标题和排版略作修改。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最近在少数派上看到这篇《最近我的工作笔记方法整理》，感觉写得非常好，但比较遗憾的是这篇讲的重点还是在「怎么记」上，「怎么查、怎么用」方面着墨较少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我一直认为，工作笔记被记录只是它发挥的第一层价值，能将每一条笔记纳入流程和体系中被不断复用，才能形成一个有生命力的笔记系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这里跟大家分享一下我的工作笔记思路。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">当代职场牛马的困境</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">作为打工人，为什么要记录工作笔记？简单来说：为了留痕复盘，为了追踪进展，为了规划时间精力，为了复用知识，为了总结汇报。最重要的是，为了让我在不工作的时候彻底忘掉工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">一句话，工作笔记要能成为你外置的工作专用的第二大脑，帮你记录、帮你回忆、帮你集中注意力，而且能快速安装和卸载。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">相信在职场工作的大家经常需要同时处理多个任务，而任务和任务之间有的有业务联系、有的则零零碎碎。这一方面要求我们能在多个业务方向中快速切换、及时响应，另一方面复杂的业务场景还要求我们对每个项目的整体脉络有清晰的把握，有能力进行长达数个月的项目跟进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">同时现代即时通信工具的特性，又导致不断有新的突发情况打断你当下的工作状态。例如同事突然找你沟通一个数周前、甚至数月前的信息。这样的「多线程+长跨度+频繁打断」的组合拳打下来，任谁都没招——作为人类的我们本质上是一种单线程的生物，注意力和记忆力都是有限的，长期的多线程任务对我们的大脑也是有害的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">因此，一套理想的工作笔记系统，应该可以支撑我们进行长周期、多线程的项目进度追踪和工作知识管理，帮助我们在任何时候都能快速且系统地回忆起任意项目的前因后果和当时的操作细节，并尽可能进行知识的复用，减少重复思考，从而让我们能在工作时更加安心的专注在当下的任务中。减轻负担、被打断了也能快速恢复，工作之外则可以放心地忘掉工作，摆脱烦恼。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">工作笔记的两条主线：时间&amp;项目</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">目前的工作笔记一般有两种思路，一种是日志型，一种是项目型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">日志型，就是以日为单位，用类似格子日记的方式分门别类地记录当天的流水和待办，每天一个文档。日志的好处在于记录方便、摩擦力小；问题则是，你会发现很多项目的工作进展和细节分散在各处，很难进行有效整合，复盘检索时极容易遗漏，对于长期的复杂项目，也难以进行整体思考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">项目型，就是每个工作任务单独建设一个文档，文档内包括这个项目内的所有前因后果、工作内容和结果产出。项目型的好处在于信息记录完整，容易整合。缺点在于一方面缺少时间上的维度，同时输入门槛高、摩擦力大，每次记录都要找对应的项目，而零散的、不属于特定项目的信息容易丢失；对于复杂的项目，可能要不断更改项目文档的结构来适应工作变化，导致最终的项目文档缺乏演变信息，丢失过程记录。每个项目之间相对独立，难以梳理多个项目之间的关联。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">因此，我考虑将两种记录方法整合起来，使得信息既可以用日志的形式进行快速记录，又可以用项目的形式进行整合，通过两种线索进行定位。接下来，我会具体讨论一下工作笔记要记什么、怎么记、怎么用。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">工作笔记的元素</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">工作笔记系统的复杂点在于，它要兼顾信息资源管理和项目管理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">信息资源管理上，工作中的多数信息包含在工作日常的流水中，例如业务动作、沟通记录、工作产出、会议纪要等流水记录。同时，在工作中也会学习、沉淀、积累一些通用的长期知识，如行业知识、工作流程（SOP）、工具和账号、关键联络人（POC）、代码和数据口径等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">项目管理方面，分为长期和短期。长期的项目管理，是指对一个复杂项目进行决策判断、路线规划、任务拆分，最终形成具体的待办事项；短期的项目管理，就是每日对所有未完成的待办任务进行当前阶段的时间、精力、资源的分配和排序，逐个执行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">所以整体流程是这样的：我们有一个长期的项目或复杂任务（如 XX 专项），它被拆分成了一个个具体的任务（如 x 月 x 日前完成设计稿/计算数据/完成代码），每日要处理的未完成的任务就是当日待办，在执行的过程中会产生新的日志记录（每日工作进展、会议纪要、个人思考、研讨结论等），中间会使用和积累各种知识资源（工具、知识、流程、联系人等）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">对应着，我们有了这个笔记系统的 4 个基本元素，也就是 4 种要记的内容：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">项目：复杂的可拆分的工作项目（自上而下），或由一系列相关任务形成的归纳结构（自下而上），用于进行长期的项目追踪概览。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">任务：拆分出的单项待办，有明确开始、结束节点和结果输出，用于聚焦在短期的待办管理。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">日志：每日新增的流水记录，是工作事件的最小颗粒度，如工作进展、会议纪要和外部事件记录，也可以记录番茄钟等短期工作区间，用于备忘和复盘。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">知识：沉淀总结下来的可复用的工作资源。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118100\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8134328358208955\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1072\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=528af248&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRiaibld4uOgWmGSOcgP87ZxcogSENQebZk2I7ACfqYicw9PQox4Ru7nwd7bqgGYWC0ZZ0ccsRuoqx2icQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <figure>\n   <figcaption style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">4 个元素的关系</span></span>\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这 4 种内容是紧密关联的，尤其是项目和任务之间并没有清晰的边界，一个简单的任务不断延伸可能逐渐成长为一个大项目；项目的层级也是不固定的，项目下的一个任务能被拆解成子任务，子任务也能不断拆分为更小的任务。因此这里的项目指的不是项目记录本身而是项目结构，是你组织工作的线索，是不断成长和变化的工作脉络。我们通过未完成的任务来确认当下聚焦的事务，通过项目结构来快速回顾工作的长期进展和前因后果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">于是我们有了 4 个核心使用场景：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. 聚焦：查看当前所有待办任务</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. 概览：回顾项目整体脉络和进展</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 记录：记录流水日志和可复用的知识</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4. 查询：查阅工作知识、工作记录、项目路线</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">有了使用场景，就可以具体设计工作笔记的模块了。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">工作笔记的模块与布局</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这里我们使用 Notion 来搭建。主要有 3 个原因：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. Notion 数据库的关联、嵌套、函数和自动化等功能一起提供了非常高的能力上限，如层级结构、自动关联、自带时间戳、动态筛选。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. Notion 的数据库和文档页面可以无缝融合，数据库内可以直接查看文档详情，文档内可以展示复杂的数据库筛选逻辑；页面布局灵活，可以在一个页面内最大化展示内容，数据库页面还可以进行侧边预览，不需要来回跳转，减少操作摩擦。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 通过数据库视图，可以做到「多处记录，一处汇总」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如前面所讲，我们有 4 种要记录的内容，其中项目和任务本质上是同一种内容，只是在结构层级上有差异，我们可以使用 Notion 数据库的「子项目」功能来构建项目结构，因此我们只需要建立 3 个数据库表：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">任务表</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">日志表</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">资源表</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">其中任务表是核心，分别与日志表和资源表关联。具体功能模块如下：</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">主页</span></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118099\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5205357142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a700a57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRiaibld4uOgWmGSOcgP87ZxcoeY1HGoyUbPsTRbN2Lp2WOYBjcfWeRDefOKPMXWappEsvl00LUm7u5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">主页布局</span></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. 日志模块：对当天流水事件的简单记录，如会议、沟通、外部事件等，也可以记录番茄钟、Timeboxing 等个人工作模块；和项目有关的日志可以关联到具体任务上。通过直接在日志内输入 /now /follow /wait /done 等指令，可以直接记录和控制关联任务的完成状态或者控制任务的优先级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. 回顾模块：以周为单位，回顾最近每日新增日志和新完成的任务，用于每周复盘和年终撰写工作总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 项目模块：项目模块是日常工作的主要空间，包括两个部分：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">项目概览：在项目模块构建项目-任务-子任务的层级构建，并进行状态维护。查阅所有已完成和未完成的工作进展。所有子任务都完成的项目会自动归档。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">待办聚焦：将项目中未完成的任务单独抽出展示，形成当日待办列表。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;background-color: transparent;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 知识管理模块：记录和查阅所有沉淀知识。这部分相对独立，依赖自己的持续维护和整理。</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">任务详情页</span></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118102\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9508928571428572\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0821dc49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRiaibld4uOgWmGSOcgP87ZxcocRXaP8nzKsYTgjPfeYMibBLZAaS9FZOjoVkLMd3QorJUS3dYsat2mug%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">任务详情页布局</span></span></h4>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. 工作详情记录：Notion 比较灵活的一点就是可以在数据库条目内继续记录文档，可以把所有的工作具体细节写在文档正文内。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. 进度日志记录：通过数据库的关联功能，分散在不同天的日志可以在日志详情页内聚合展示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 项目结构编辑：通过筛选，可以只显示</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">当前任务所在的项目树，并进行项目结构的维护。关于如何筛选特定的项目树，可以参考我的&nbsp;</span><a class=\"weapp_text_link js_weapp_entry\" style=\"\" data-unique-id=\"mjch1t71-q9inl2\" data-miniprogram-type=\"text\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wx61fbcef671fd833b\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/post/index?id=10137\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"少数派\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">另一篇文章</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">最后的一点讨论</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">可不可以不用 Notion？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">当然是可以的，一些双链笔记也可以做到通过反向链接实现将零散的日志通过项目聚合，有的也支持通过数据库管理待办（如 Obsidian 的一些插件）。我不是来卖模版的（笑），所以欢迎大家尝试在不同工具软件上实践这套方法，并和我分享。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">为什么要做这么复杂？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">总的来说有 3 个原因：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. 零散的记录难以产生价值，且容易被遗忘，需要通过线索来梳理和索引。使用「时间+项目」的双维度对记录进行定位，可以最大化的发挥工作日志的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. 项目结构通常是在实际工作中逐渐生长出来的，多层级数据库可以在对项目进行结构化的情况下保证最大的灵活度；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 待办聚焦+项目概览，可以让你快速在工作模式和思考模式之间切换。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">其实，很多专业的项目管理工具上都可以进行单个项目的拆分概览和跨项目的未完成任务汇总，有的还附带每天的工时统计，可以将精确到小时分钟的工作时间关联到具体待办上，但附带日志功能的则不太常见（也可能是我孤陋寡闻）。况且很多项目管理软件更偏向协作和规划，目的并不在于记录和知识管理，对于个人使用来说还是太重了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这套工作笔记系统更加侧重记录和归纳，方便事后的复盘和汇报，弱化了事前的计划。我个人觉得，详实的记录可以减轻头脑的负担，过度的计划则容易带来焦虑。公司里老板对你的计划已经够多了，自己还是尽量放过自己吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/103960?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspai.com/post/103960?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：</span><span leaf=\"\">清垚土土土</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编：克莱德</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章提出了一种结合时间线和项目管理双维度的 Notion 高效工作笔记系统，旨在解决职场人多任务、长周期、易打断的工作困境，实现记录、复用、追溯与回顾的平衡。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章提出了一种结合时间线和项目管理双维度的 Notion 高效工作笔记系统，旨在解决职场人多任务、长周期、易打断的工作困境，实现记录、复用、追溯与回顾的平衡。",
  "summary": "文章分享了一种基于时间维度（日志）与项目维度（任务、项目）相结合的工作笔记思路，核心在于将“怎么记”与“怎么查、怎么用”有效融合，建立一个有生命力的笔记系统。作者分析了当代职场人“多线程+长跨度+频繁打断”的工作困境，指出传统日志型和项目型笔记的局限性。随后，文章引入以 Notion 为工具，搭建包含“任务表”、“日志表”和“资源表”的笔记模块，并通过主页布局和任务详情页展示了如何实现任务聚焦、项目概览、流水记录和知识查询四大核心使用场景，最终帮助职场人减轻大脑负担，提高工作效率。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
